<p><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/\"><strong>About The PM Group</strong></a>: The PM Group was founded in 1988. For over 32 years, the agency has continued to grow and is San Antonio’s largest advertising agency. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala that to date has raised millions of dollars for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years! In the past 10 years, The PM Group has raised both directly and indirectly over $12 million for these charities. It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"A Look Back at our Spookiest Halloween Festivities","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"A Look Back at our Spookiest Halloween Festivities","url":"/a-look-back-at-our-spookiest-halloween-festivities/"}],"title":"A Look Back at our Spookiest Halloween Festivities | The PM Group","metaDesc":"As an advertising agency with several other creative sister agencies in the mix, you can bet the spookiest time of the year gets over the top...","focuskw":"Halloween","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"A Look Back at our Spookiest Halloween Festivities | The PM Group","opengraphDescription":"As an advertising agency with several other creative sister agencies in the mix, you can bet the spookiest time of the year gets over the top...","opengraphImage":{"altText":"","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Image-10.30.20-Halloween.png","srcSet":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Image-10.30.20-Halloween-300x158.png 300w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Image-10.30.20-Halloween-1024x538.png 1024w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Image-10.30.20-Hallowe